item.description: Alright it's that time of year again. We are going to meet at the beach again for some great volleyball. We will be putting up the net at 3:30pm and starting soon after setup. Negative behavior is not permitted. We should all help putting up the net if we are available. We should all be having fun! Please everyone that can help putting up the net it would be much appreciated.  It would also be great if a couple people could bring a rake. If you are new to this we would love you to join.  Let's hope the weather is nice and sunny! New people are always welcome and don't hesitate to email me with questions. If you have a rake bring it please. After we go out for drinks at a local bar.
item.how_to_find_us: We will be there setting up the volleyball net! Let us know you are there and we will welcome you!
